data.description: Nestled at the cul-de-sac's end, this home offers serenity and seclusion. Its sprawling private lot includes an inviting in-ground concrete pool and a spacious concrete patio, all bordered by a tranquil wooded backdrop. The kitchen, freshly renovated and painted, sparkles with modernity and style. Recent upgrades ensure peace of mind: a brand-new roof this year, HVAC and electric panel replacement in 2020, and a new water heater in 2019. This property resides in a highly sought-after neighborhood, promising a sense of community.  Convenience is key, with the city center, CNU, and I-64 just moments away. Don't let this rare opportunity slip away—schedule a viewing now and make this exceptional home yours!
